  <brief_title>Chemotherapy in Treating Patients With Newly Diagnosed Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia Trial 4: A Randomized Comparison of Chlorambucil, Fludarabine and Fludarabine Plus Cyclophosphamide</official_title>
